{"tid":2424904,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 豉 油 王 炒 麵 ］附好用新煲  有圖","createTime":"2021-02-27T03:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T01:04:14.000Z","uid":227988,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"edcf6f191928e71c6d1475ab6a2e86a4a451d12e","tid":2424904,"uid":227988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"炒左幾次，最好食今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用左2個全蛋麵炒  幾香<br />\n加少少豬油炒  再香啲<br />\n 拎隻鉗 拎到廚房嘅感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n豉油汁：<br />\n生抽 1 湯匙 <br />\n老抽 1 湯匙    <br />\n蠔油 1/2 湯匙<br />\n糖 1茶匙 <br />\n雞粉 （可選）<br />\n胡椒粉 （可選）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fjam6mx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjam6mx.png&h=3a375908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煲好用， 應該要入十大廚具之一<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUwYo8h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUwYo8h.png&h=fea7feda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZDshtn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZDshtn.png&h=d895e312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4sBRYPtI1gQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4sBRYPtI1gQ&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=ccf18444\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4sBRYPtI1gQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mytableeee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmytableeee&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=20944bcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/mytableeee</a>"},{"pid":"a478c85cdecbcac6094098413ca2af8bbc847939","tid":2424904,"uid":227988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"如果汁太杰，可以加幾滴水"},{"pid":"34f70b3842a6cf98346299f6e12b43d2f57cf182","tid":2424904,"uid":3